(227, 453, 2, 4, '2025-07-07', 'HW- Drawing and coloring', 'I fly without wings, I have feathers but I’m not a bird — hit me over the net if you’ve heard!\r\n(What am I? → Shuttlecock or birdie)\r\n\r\nI’m light, I’m fast, I swing in your hand — serve me up to take a stand!\r\n(What am I? → Badminton racket)\r\n\r\nTwo or four players, a net in the middle — we smash, we serve, and solve the riddle!\r\n(What game is this? → Badminton)\r\n\r\nI’m not a smash cake, but I smash with power — aiming down to win this hour!\r\n(What move am I? → Smash)\r\n\r\nYou serve me high, I glide through the sky — sometimes I drop and make opponents cry!\r\n(Who am I? → Shuttlecock)\r\n\r\nI’m fast, I’m fierce, I fly like a spark — play me inside, not in the park.\r\n(What game am I? → Badminton)', '/uploads/homework/1751900017_bATMINTION.png'),
