(158, 178, 'New Homework Assigned', 'You have a new homework assignment:\n“June Week 1 - World Environment Day – June 5th. Repeat the CW”\nWorld Environment Day – June 5th.\r\n\r\n\r\nWorld Environment Day is celebrated every year on June 5th to raise awareness and take action for the protection of our environment. It was started by the United Nations in 1972, and each year focuses on a different theme related to nature and the planet’s health.\r\n\r\nWhy It Matters:\r\n\r\nIt reminds us to reduce pollution, save trees, conserve water, and protect wildlife.\r\n\r\nEvery small step—like planting a tree, reducing plastic use, or saving electricity—can help.\r\n\r\nThe Earth is our only home. Keeping it clean and green is our responsibility.', 0, '2025-06-18 04:16:44'),
